    "media_with_content_cpwzVU": {
      "type": "media-with-content",
      "blocks": {
        "text_content_bzmDUi": {
          "type": "text_content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Product Details",
            "description": "<p>BioRepair+ Face Oil is your daily skin ritual—designed to restore balance, bounce, and glow in one silky step. Powered by our Mānuka BioRepair+ complex, this nutrient-rich blend helps replenish essential lipids, support barrier strength, and calm visible reactivity.<br/><br/>Formulated with over 20 potent botanical oils—rich in antioxidants, fatty acids, and bioactives—it hydrates deeply, smooths texture, and brings skin back to its most radiant, resilient self.<br/><br/>Fast-absorbing, non-comedogenic, and ultra-nourishing, it’s skincare that works quietly but powerfully—for skin that’s ready to feel strong, calm, and radiant—every day.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_content_im6CWf": {
          "type": "text_content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Ingredients",
            "description": "<p><strong>Directions for use:</strong><br/>Start with clean, dry skin. Apply 3-5 drops of BioRepair+ Face Oil to your face, neck, and décolletage. Gently tap the oil into the skin for quick absorption, or massage in upward strokes for added relaxation and circulation. For best results, use morning and night as the final step in your skincare routine.<br/><br/><strong>Ingredients:</strong><br/>Mānuka Biorepair+Complex (Leptospermum scoparium (Mānuka) Oil, Kunzea ericoides (Kānuka) Oil, Phormium tenax (Harakeke) Seed Oil, Macropiper excelsum (Kawakawa) Extract), Squalane, Vitis vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil, Carthamus tinctorius (Safflower) Oil, Limnanthes alba (Meadowfoam) Seed Oil, Calophyllum inophyllum (Tamanu) Oil, Ribes nigrum (Blackcurrant) Seed Oil, Vaccinium macrocarpon (Cranberry) Seed Oil, Lycium barbarum (Goji) Seed Oil, Hippophae rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) Fruit Oil, Opuntia ficus-indica (Prickly Pear) Seed Oil, Oenothera biennis (Evening Primrose) Oil, Tanacetum annuum (Blue Tansy) Oil, Boswellia carterii (Frankincense) Oil, Rosa canina (Rosehip) Oil, Rosa damascena (Damascus Rose) Essential Oil, Daucus carota (Carrot Seed) Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Rosmarinus officinalis (Rosemary), CO2 Extract.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_content_6kdRGF": {
          "type": "collapsible_content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "FAQ",
            "row_heading_1": "When and how should I use BioRepair+?",
            "row_content_1": "<p>Use BioRepair+ morning and night, after cleansing and any water-based serums or toners. Apply a few drops to clean, slightly damp skin and gently press into the face, neck, and chest. You can follow with moisturizer if your skin needs extra hydration, or let the oil be your final step.</p>",
            "row_heading_2": "Where does BioRepair+ fit in my skincare routine?",
            "row_content_2": "<p>We recommend applying BioRepair+ after serums and before (or instead of) moisturizer.<br/><br/><em><strong>Suggested order:</strong></em><br/>1. Cleanser<br/>2. Toner or mist (optional)<br/>3. Water-based serums<br/>4. BioRepair+ Face Oil<br/>5. Moisturizer (if desired)</p>",
            "row_heading_3": "Will BioRepair+ clog my pores?",
            "row_content_3": "<p>No — BioRepair+ is formulated with non-comedogenic, fast-absorbing botanical oils that nourish without congestion.<br/><br/>It features native New Zealand botanicals like Mānuka, Kānuka, Harakeke, and Kawakawa, which are known for their anti-inflammatory and balancing properties. These work alongside lightweight oils like squalane, rosehip, grape seed, and prickly pear to restore and repair — without heaviness.</p>",
            "row_heading_4": "Can I use BioRepair+ under makeup?",
            "row_content_4": "<p>Yes. BioRepair+ absorbs beautifully and creates a smooth, hydrated base for makeup. Just allow a few minutes for full absorption before applying SPF or foundation.</p>",
            "row_heading_5": "Is BioRepair+ suitable for sensitive skin?",
            "row_content_5": "<p>Yes — BioRepair+ is designed to support sensitive and barrier-compromised skin. Its botanical blend helps calm, soothe, and strengthen.<br/><br/>However, all skin is unique. We recommend doing a patch test before your first use, especially if you're sensitive to essential oils or plant extracts. Apply a small amount behind your ear or on your inner wrist and monitor for 24 hours. Discontinue use if irritation occurs.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
